  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\nModify the drag gesture recogniser so that it covers the entire area of the bottom sheet component, and not only the top 16px handle. Initiating the drag gesture should be possible from any X,Y coordinate inside the sheet. Here's a [link to a longer recording of what I mean](https://www.dropbox.com/s/n8uhr3ueflw3fhw/BottomSheet.mp4?dl=0)\r\n\r\nPreview\r\n\r\n![BottomSheet](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4932774/72616531-79f05700-3937-11ea-98c8-347d316158fb.gif)\r\n\r\n### Acceptance Criteria\r\n\r\nGood: Can start dragging the bottom sheet from any position.\r\nBad: Can start dragging the bottom sheet only from the short top handle.\r\n\r\n### Notes\r\n\r\nA few of our bottom sheets have scrollable content inside. Scroll should always override the drag gesture.\r\nüôè you're awesome üôè \r\n",
